title: 82. Horsepower Or Horsesh*t: It's Your Choice
itunes:title: 82. Horsepower Or Horsesh*t: It's Your Choice
description: Are you pulling the wagon, riding in the wagon, or criticizing from the sidelines? On today's episode, Andy explains how Clydesdales help us understand the three kinds of people in this world, which one you should avoid, and the one that will yield the best results.
